<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Because_You_Loved_Me&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Sales and chart performance">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sales_and_chart_performance">Sales and chart performance</span></h2>
<p>It reached number 1 in the United States (6 weeks at the top), Australia (3 weeks) and Canada (1 week). In all of these countries, it was her second number 1 song, after "<a href="The_Power_of_Love_(Jennifer_Rush_song)#C.C3.A9line_Dion_version" title="The Power of Love (Jennifer Rush song)">The Power of Love</a>." The single set a record on the U.S. <a href="Hot_Adult_Contemporary_Tracks" title="Hot Adult Contemporary Tracks" class="mw-redirect">Hot Adult Contemporary Tracks</a>, where it remained at number 1 for 19 weeks. It topped many other American charts as well, including <a href="Billboard_Hot_100_Airplay" title="Billboard Hot 100 Airplay" class="mw-redirect">Billboard Hot 100 Airplay</a> (14 weeks at the top) and <a href="Hot_100_Singles_Sales" title="Hot 100 Singles Sales" class="mw-redirect">Hot 100 Singles Sales</a> (6 weeks), also <a href="Hot_Adult_Top_40_Tracks" title="Hot Adult Top 40 Tracks" class="mw-redirect">Hot Adult Top 40 Tracks</a> (12 weeks) and <a href="Top_40_Mainstream" title="Top 40 Mainstream" class="mw-redirect">Top 40 Mainstream</a> (5 weeks). "Because You Loved Me" was also a hit in the rest of the world reaching number 2 in Ireland, number 3 in New Zealand and Switzerland, number 4 in the Netherlands, number 5 in the United Kingdom and Belgium etc.</p>
<p>According to <a href="Billboard_Magazine" title="Billboard Magazine" class="mw-redirect">Ask Billboard</a>, the physical copy of the single has sold 1,343,000 copies and the digital copy of the single has sold 704,000 units since being available bringing total sales to 2,047,000 copies sold in the US.<sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> The single is certified platinum in the US. It was also certified 2x platinum in Australia (140,000), platinum in New Zealand (10,000), gold in Germany (250,000) and silver in the United Kingdom (although it has sold 420,000 copies and should be certified gold). Also in France, "Because You Loved Me" has sold 195,000 copies and should be certified silver.</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Because_You_Loved_Me&action=edit&section=2.php.html" title="Edit section: Awards and nominations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Awards_and_nominations">Awards and nominations</span></h2>
<p>The song was nominated for an <a href="Academy_Award" title="Academy Award">Academy Award</a> and a <a href="Golden_Globe_Award" title="Golden Globe Award">Golden Globe Award</a>, as well as four <a href="Grammy_Award" title="Grammy Award">Grammy Awards</a>. It won a <a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Song_Written_for_a_Motion_Picture,_Television_or_Other_Visual_Media" title="Grammy Award for Best Song Written for a Motion Picture, Television or Other Visual Media" class="mw-redirect">Grammy Award for Best Song Written for a Motion Picture, Television or Other Visual Media</a> (award went to Diane Warren), and was nominated for the <a href="Grammy_Award_for_Record_of_the_Year" title="Grammy Award for Record of the Year">Record of the Year</a>, <a href="Grammy_Award_for_Song_of_the_Year" title="Grammy Award for Song of the Year">Song of the Year</a> and <a href="Grammy_Award_for_Best_Female_Pop_Vocal_Performance" title="Grammy Award for Best Female Pop Vocal Performance">Best Female Pop Vocal Performance</a>.</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Because_You_Loved_Me&action=edit&section=3.php.html" title="Edit section: Music video">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Music_video">Music video</span></h2>
<p>A music video was created for the song, which showed Dion singing interspersed with clips from the film <i>Up Close &amp; Personal</i>. It was directed by <a href="Kevin_Bray_(director)" title="Kevin Bray (director)">Kevin Bray</a> in January 1996 and released in February.</p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Because_You_Loved_Me&action=edit&section=4.php.html" title="Edit section: Formats and track listings">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Formats_and_track_listings">Formats and track listings</span></h2>
