<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Because_You_Loved_Me&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: Covers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Covers">Covers</span></h2>
<p>In 1997, Dominican singer <a href="Milly_Quezada" title="Milly Quezada">Milly Quezada</a> released a Spanish version of the song titled "Porque Me Amaste" on her album <i>Hasta Siempre</i>. This version peaked at #29 on the <a href="Hot_Latin_Songs" title="Hot Latin Songs"><i>Billboard</i> Hot Latin Songs</a> chart and #4 on the <a href="Tropical_Songs" title="Tropical Songs"><i>Billboard</i> Tropical Songs</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-33" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-33"><span>[</span>33<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p>The track was also covered by <a href="Johnny_Mathis" title="Johnny Mathis">Johnny Mathis</a> (1998), <a href="Michael_Ball_(singer)" title="Michael Ball (singer)">Michael Ball</a> (1998), <a href="Vivian_Reed_(musical_theatre_actress)" title="Vivian Reed (musical theatre actress)">Vivian Reed</a> (2001), <a href="Jane_McDonald" title="Jane McDonald">Jane McDonald</a> (2001), <a href="Siti_Nurhaliza" title="Siti Nurhaliza">Siti Nurhaliza</a> (2005), <a href="Clay_Aiken" title="Clay Aiken">Clay Aiken</a> (2006), Miho Fukuhara (2007), <a href="Nina_Girado" title="Nina Girado">Nina Girado</a> (2008) and <a href="Diamond_White" title="Diamond White" class="mw-redirect">Diamond White</a> who performed the song on the X Factor USA 2012.<sup id="cite_ref-34" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-34"><span>[</span>34<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p>The Song was also covered by Glee in the Episode "<a href="Props_(Glee)" title="Props (Glee)">Props</a>" by <a href="Jenna_Ushkowitz" title="Jenna Ushkowitz">Jenna Ushkowitz</a> as <a href="Tina_Cohen-Chang" title="Tina Cohen-Chang">Tina Cohen-Chang</a> as <a href="Rachel_Berry" title="Rachel Berry">Rachel Berry</a>.</p>
<p>Another popular cover was recorded by singer Ana Laura for her self-titled debut.</p>
